-- Sender dependent relayhost.
--  - per-user: account='user@domain.com'
--  - per-domain: account='@domain.com'
-- References:
--  - http://www.postfix.org/postconf.5.html#sender_dependent_relayhost_maps
--  - http://www.postfix.org/transport.5.html
